Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大户爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这么晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,梦不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现实才更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次免费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下次把钱包带来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心  你肯定喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这扭蛋很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,特别？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,里面装着你想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有什么想要的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别骗人了  当然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是该冷藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是还活着  是不是应该保温才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  说不定会把它煮熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它能打破吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说  我可以打破它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把包放下  你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爱！老师来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大户妈妈  不用勉强叫她起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来送这周的讲义的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.64,Top,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.27,Top,,0,0,0,,总是麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.90,Top,,0,0,0,,没有没有  不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:32.40,Top,,0,0,0,,我只是回家路上来看看罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,里面是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再到那里去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我会在学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不搞大点她不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…  那就再多加点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？你还说是我做得过火呢  你个魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给在学校的各位提问：
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要是班上有人被欺凌该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没错！正确答案当然是视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大户爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打破蛋  把蛋打破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是奇妙蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快点打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这很硬  我打不破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快点打破！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,打破！打破它！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不是做得挺好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  为什么要在这种地方打破啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是完事了  就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也不需要用这种口气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,高高在上让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,用普通的语气不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说我也应声了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要跑咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.88,Default,,800,0,0,,那个… 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,800,0,,要快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是「视而不见」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是肝脏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是梦  一场噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看看你的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的伤口不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说这是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但对我来说这是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,总之  在打铃之前我们要一直跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只追我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了你在这个世界是不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你的眼睛和心脏没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那还叫不死身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌  为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你买了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我没买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,说是第一个免费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是么  没什么比免费更贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你没有朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是没有  是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就不会打破蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过表面朋友也是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,「是啊是啊」「我知道」「好可爱」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只会这样附和的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我没有挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回想起来  挚友真的很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友会分手  但挚友是一辈子的事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你有过男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我先问的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们「一二」一起说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍赖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,错的是它们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的  它们不来追我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不来追我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫长濑小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那长濑同学就坐大户同学的旁边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起回家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,「诶」是什么反应啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太伤人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里这么清静  是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大户同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我在一起不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是丑女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不丑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛又大又圆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的发型？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要遮住这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的伞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,爱  你朋友来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我朋友  我没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你忘记的东西送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,双眼虹膜颜色不一样  这叫做异色瞳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,常见于猫和狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真是神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得没必要藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道我因此受欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,做挚友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是不行…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能做挚友  我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我辜负了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我交到的第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一点  就差一点就要打铃了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,人行横道  即使和人群一起过也很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再视而不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经怒不可遏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫西城胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大户爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,爱… 该告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘记我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,得救的就只有你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想把挚友找回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有点温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我保护了胡桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  要是我保护更多的人  小糸就能复活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爱  来吃饭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天气特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要总是睡在床上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我把洗的衣服晾起来了  下午帮忙收回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.04,Top,,0,0,0,,呀  都已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此  我在那边是不死身  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈今天早上要开会  所以现在就得出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,午餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会是晚上溜出去在外面被卷入什么事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  伤情怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,钱包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要保护多少人小糸才能复活？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,唯独这件事  我没法告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果同时保护多个人  那就会更快一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是个贪婪的小笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要是没保护好  你也没法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  敌人也不全是那么容易对付
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟它们只是「视而不见」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一群乌合之众
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你的挚友一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在某个世界里变成了雕像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,除非她的朋友去到那个世界  不然她就永远那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃她也自杀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是大号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你左边的是小号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有别的客人先来了  你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  还有其他人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也一直很担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,身材好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,待续
